#. Tag: title
#: man-ghostwriter.1.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Opis"

#. Tag: para
#: man-ghostwriter.1.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>ghostwriter</command> is a Qt text editing application for Markdown "
"that provides an aesthetic, distraction-free writing environment."
msgstr ""
"<command>ghostwriter</command> je aplikacija za urejanje besedila Qt za "
"Markdown, ki zagotavlja estetsko okolje za pisanje brez motenj."

#. Tag: para
#: man-ghostwriter.1.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Create your own custom themes, write in fullscreen mode, or use focus mode "
"to concentrate on just one or more lines."
msgstr ""
"Ustvarite lastne teme po meri, pišite v celozaslonskem načinu ali uporabite "
"način ostrenja, da se osredotočite samo na eno ali več vrstic."

#. Tag: para
#: man-ghostwriter.1.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A live HTML preview allows you to view the final formatting as you type. "
"HTML preview and export options are provided by the built-in Markdown "
"processor, cmark-gfm; but you may add more by installing Pandoc, "
"MultiMarkdown, or cmark processors. The application will automatically "
"detect their installation if their locations are in the system's PATH "
"environment variable."
msgstr ""
"Predogled HTML v živo vam omogoča ogled končnega oblikovanja med tipkanjem. "
"Možnosti predogleda in izvoza HTML zagotavlja vgrajen procesor Markdown, "
"cmark-gfm; vendar lahko dodate več z namestitvijo procesorjev Pandoc, "
"MultiMarkdown ali cmark. Aplikacija bo samodejno zaznala njihovo namestitev, "
"če so njihove lokacije v sistemski spremenljivki okolja PATH."

